NetMessagingBindingCollectionElement Class

Definition

Represents a configuration element that contains sub-elements that specify settings for using the NetMessagingBinding binding.

In this Article

public sealed class NetMessagingBindingCollectionElement : System.ServiceModel.Configuration.StandardBindingCollectionElement<Microsoft.ServiceBus.Messaging.NetMessagingBinding,Microsoft.ServiceBus.Messaging.Configuration.NetMessagingBindingExtensionElement>

NetMessagingBindingCollectionElement

Initializes a new instance of the NetMessagingBindingCollectionElement class.
